text: Vincent Ramaël (born 22 June 1988) is a French professional footballer who plays for UE Sant Julià in the Andorran Primera Divisió. ==Career== Ramaël was born in Clamart, France. He began his career with Belgian side Excelsior Mouscron, where he signed his first professional contract on 31 August 2006.Ramael signe son 1er contrat pro On 26 September 2006, he joined AS Monaco FC.Ramaël quitte l'Excelsior! He joined A.F.C. Tubize on loan on 18 July 2008.Officiel : Ramaël prêté à Tubize before returning to Monaco on 12 January 2009.Ramael vers un retour à Monaco For the 2011–12 season he was signed by Belgian Third Division club Royal Geants Athois. ==References== ==External links== * * Footgoal Profile Category:Living people Category:1988 births Category:People from Clamart Category:Association football forwards Category:French footballers Category:A.F.C.
